node.text:
Try this on your phone!😱🔥

Step-by-step tutorial:

1️⃣ Take a photo
2️⃣ Download a background image
3️⃣ Open the app ‘Snapseed’
4️⃣ Import your photo
5️⃣ Select ‘Double Exposure’ (Tools > Double Exposure) and click ‘Add an image’ (first icon)
6️⃣ Select your background image
7️⃣ Click ‘Opacity’ (third icon) and set the opacity to 100%
8️⃣ Select ‘View edits’ (top right, first icon)
9️⃣ Click ‘Double Exposure’ and select the brush tool
🔟 Mask the background
—————————————
🎥| @arianteo
—————————————
